reviews.text: This game is amazing and super fun, but there is a couple things. I‚Äôve been playing this since it came out and I have over 12GB of data on it b/c I can‚Äôt get rid of anything. I would love to sell a bunch of camos for guns and skins that I don‚Äôt use anymore. We could sell them as an option for cod points or credits depending on the value it holds like common to legendary. And the lag is kinda bad, meaning it doesn‚Äôt happen all the time. In Battle Royals I would get random lag spikes and sometimes it would just lag out for like 10 seconds or more. I would lag back in and be dead. It‚Äôs really frustrating trying to get to legendary when you keep lagging out even with good service. Overall this game is really great but the less I have that I don‚Äôt use, the faster the game runs. The action and graphics are great in this game for a MOBILE game. Y‚Äôall did a really good job on this; just need to add a sell option.

reviews.name: It‚Äôs fine.
reviews.title: It‚Äôs fine.
reviews.text: It‚Äôs fine. It‚Äôs fun enough to play, it‚Äôs not *entirely* pay to win, although the amount of stuff you can only buy with real money is a bit excessive, it‚Äôs mostly all cosmetic and mostly doesn‚Äôt give any real in game advantages. It‚Äôs fairly buggy and with the latest update, at least for me, the lag has picked up quite a bit, but it‚Äôs mostly just annoying stuff (except for the scope on my Rytec is broken in every game mode no matter what, it just shows up hot pink and you can‚Äôt see through it. When you look down the sites you can still see your reticle, but other than that it‚Äôs just a hot pink blob and it makes using the gun impossible. TMI I know). Despite all of the bugs and the lagginess and the certifiably toxic player base, it‚Äôs still a fun game though. I recommend it, just with a little bit of caution.
